2-1 降维打击3F：要事第一 分级聚焦（Focus）

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appbGXMXHMv8623/v_5a530dc95480b_qyBHmrc4

<section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.5em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">01 谁还没在工作生活中遇到过“烦乱”？</p></section></section></section></section><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">你一早安安分分，9:00准时坐在办公位上，打开电脑，登录微信PC端，登上QQ，打开邮箱，翻开工作记录本，准备踏踏实实开展一天的工作时。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">这时：<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">主管A突然到访，上面来了新指示，即将进行新项目，啥时候有空，赶紧先开个会。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">紧接着，同事B拿着昨天你交给他的方案要就上面的说明1和2跟你探讨。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">总算看你没人找了，下属C也是战战兢兢地向你走来，态度温顺地跟你请教，这个不会写，那个也不会做……</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">当你好不容易处理完了ABC，或者做好了处理ABC的计划，这才发现工作记录上的DEF还没有任何着落……<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">要知道，即便没有这些个ABC，DEF的打扰，在信息发达，时间碎片化的当下，已经有够多的事情会阻碍我们的注意力了。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 2px 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: -3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 4px; transform: rotate(0deg); float: left; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section></section><section style="margin: -2px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border-top: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); border-right-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-bottom-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); border-left-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 601px; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 3px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(237, 161, 60); text-align: left; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: none; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">“即使当我们独自工作，门也关上了，没人让我们分心，不知何故总之，我们就是很有办法让自己分心。诱惑也许来自刚收到的一封电子邮件；或是追求完美的强大念头，让我们面对一个看起来丑陋的苦差事，无法坚持下去；即便工作卖力但成效不彰，又苦思不出对策时放弃的念头更是排山倒海而来。每当我们试着完成有意义并且是高标准的事情时，这些都是我们经历过常见的分心。”——彼得·布雷格曼&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 《微时间管理术》作者</p></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 601px; text-align: right; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: -2px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; height: 4px; float: right; transform: rotate(0deg); background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 100%; float: left; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"></section><section style="margin: 