了3年，眼看就要拖够第4年；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">压力倍增的时候，老觉着要出去旅个游，散散心，可就连周末逛个公园的时间好像也没有；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">父母要花时间陪一下，老婆老公也要花时间陪一下，孩子更要陪，没有孩子也得陪陪猫猫狗狗吧？！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">要知道，连陪伴关怀一下自己的时间都没有。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">……<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/88173500_1515392079.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hcphm4dmbzknoelyi1cy74qid98lsgnrv8qe1e2unugavib7zpjaicpic4m3c2qmmjfdvjy0mqxshic9nnbbiaecsa/640" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">最终，我们降低要求，不为了像那些存在于网络宣传当中的“大神们”，“大咖们”一样实现斜杠，或者是多任务处理，只想顺顺利利完成每一个工作任务，平平稳稳解决每一个生活难题，只想多一点点对自己工作、生活的切实的掌控感，这很难么？！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-bottom-left-radius: 0.5em; border-bottom-right-radius: 0.5em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">02 难的是没有方法，或有方法不实践</p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">解决这个问题，其实一点也不难。韩寒那句“反鸡汤”人人都会讲“听过很多道理，却依然过不好这一生”。原因很简单，可能你听的道理还是不够多，或者你只是听了却没有做。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">结构思考力学院在线学习平台杏壳，联合标准梦工厂共同推出《14天项目管理（善管）思维训练营——人人都能掌握的项目管理精髓》。给你方法，带你实践！</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.8em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; border-radius: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(237, 161, 60); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;">学什么？</p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/61512500_1515392395.png" title=".png" alt="微信图片_20180108101338.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); text-align: center;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAUaBYivz8405/image/ueditor/67570900_1515392202.png" title=".png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">从确认目标开始，逐一拆解工作任务，生活难题，从模型入手，一步一动，顺势而为，轻松化解复杂情境，重拾工作人生掌控权。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);">课程知识点，将以视频的方式出现，训练营将给出阶段性学习任务要求，具体进度和学习时间，学员可灵活自由安排。<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; 